âš™ï¸ Installation Steps
Clone the repository:

bash
Copy
Edit
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/PageTurner-Ecommerce-Bookshop.git
Import the database:

Open phpMyAdmin

Create a new database named pageturner

Import the pageturner.sql file from the database folder

Configure database in config.php:

$host = "localhost";
$user = "root";
$pass = "";
$db = "pageturner";
$conn = mysqli_connect($host, $user, $pass, $db);
Run the project:

Start Apache and MySQL using XAMPP/WAMP

Visit http://localhost/PageTurner



